Oil Slides in London as Libyan Rebels Enter Tripoli, New York Crude Rises

-- B y   B e n   S h a r p l e s
-- 
2011-08-22T01:38:45Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-22/oil-slides-in-london-as-libyan-rebels-enter-tripoli-new-york-crude-rises.html
Oil futures rose 0.4 percent in  New
York , paring earlier losses, to trade at $82.70 a barrel. Brent
crude slumped 1.6 percent to $106.92, narrowing the premium to
U.S. prices from a record settlement on Aug. 19.  To contact the reporter on this story:
